snippet.title: FIST OF JESUS THE GAME: TRAILER FOR STEAM
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD HERE http://store.steampowered.com/app/321110
WATCH THE SHORT FILM: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GuKV2Z3eYTY

Brothers, how the Old Testament predicted 17th October the zombies plague will come to STEAM. Help Jesus and Judas to exterminate all the zombies and restore peace in the world. 
Download now the most gore and wild game of the moment "Fist of Jesus: The bloody gospel of Judas"
http://store.steampowered.com/app/321110

Hermanos, tal y cómo predijo el Antiguo Testamento el 17 de Octubre llegará la plaga zombies a STEAM. Ayuda a Jesús y Judas a exterminar la plaga de Zombies y consigue restablecer la paz en el mundo. 
Descarga ahora el videojuego más gore y salvaje del momento "FIST of Jesus: The bloody gospel of Judas"
